==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fullness
<hw>Full"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state of being full, or of
abounding; abundance; completeness.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>fulness</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>⟦ldquo⟧In thy presence is <qex>fullness</qex> of joy.⟦rdquo⟧</q>
<rj><qau>Ps. xvi. 11.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>full-of-the-moon</ent>⟦br⟧
